title: Jeremy Jones - Signatures series #2 - Product review
description:
In development for nearly a decade with the world's premier big mountain rider, we present the Jones 3L Jacket. Uncompromising in it's quest for backcountry riding perfection, but still looking stylish on the hill, the Jones 3L is the only Jacket Jeremy trusts in the backcountry.

Jones 3l Pant: http://eu.oneill.com/en/jones-3l-shel...
